## 7. Professional Development Concepts

### 7.1 Code Organization

**File Structure Principles:**
- Feature-based organization
- Separation of concerns
- Reusable component libraries
- Utility function organization

**Import/Export Patterns:**
- Named exports for utilities
- Default exports for components
- Barrel exports for clean imports
- Dynamic imports for code splitting

### 7.2 Performance Optimization

**React Performance Concepts:**
- Component memoization with React.memo
- Callback memoization with useCallback
- Value memoization with useMemo
- Virtual DOM optimization

**State Management Performance:**
- Minimize unnecessary re-renders
- Use efficient state update patterns
- Implement proper dependency arrays
- Avoid inline object creation

### 7.3 Error Handling and Debugging

**Error Boundary Implementation:**
- Catch JavaScript errors in component tree
- Display fallback UI for better UX
- Log errors for debugging
- Prevent application crashes

**Debugging Strategies:**
- React DevTools usage
- Console logging best practices
- Network request debugging
- State management debugging

### 7.4 Testing Concepts

**Testing Strategies:**
- Unit testing for individual components
- Integration testing for component interactions
- End-to-end testing for user workflows
- Snapshot testing for UI consistency

**Testing Tools:**
- Jest for unit testing
- React Testing Library for component testing
- Cypress for end-to-end testing
- Mock Service Worker for API mocking

